1948,"June 28","1948 Fukui earthquake strikes Fukui, Japan. 3,769 dead, 22,203 injured."
1948,"July 26","U.S. President Truman signs [i]Executive Order 9981[/i], ending racial segregation in the United States Armed Forces."
