1949,"May 23","The Federal Republic of Germany is established."
1949,"September 6","Allied military authorities relinquish control of former Nazi Germany assets back to Germany."
1949,"September 13","The Soviet Union vetoes United Nations membership for Ceylon, Finland, Iceland, Italy, Jordan and Portugal."
